{"ID":"20250828100117-xv18wda","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250828100117-xv18wda","title":"密码和密钥","type":"doc","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-xq04nea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-xq04nea","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信息安全的讨论中，绕不过密码（Password）和密钥（key）两个概念。怎么理解这两个概念呢？简单说："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-24lb8sl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-24lb8sl","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密码（Password）：人类可以记住和输入的字符串，比如，由字母和数字组成的账户登录密码。eg：Kaixinguo123321"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-4ncc52g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-4ncc52g","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密钥（Key）：用于加密算法（如AES）的二进制数据，具有固定长度和强度要求。eg：0x112233445566778899AABBCCDDEEFFA5"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-pgsgxtk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-pgsgxtk","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然密码可以用于身份验证，但它们通常不适合直接作为加密算法的密钥使用。 这又是为什么呢？本文就这个话题展开讨论。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-7uayafp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-7uayafp","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、密码不能作为密钥使用的原因"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-qc8lasa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-qc8lasa","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密码的强度和格式不一定满足加密算法（如AES-128）对密钥的要求，比如，密钥可能要求长度必须是128位，且具有足够的熵（随机性）。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-et50rbj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-et50rbj","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（一）密码强度"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-egao5r0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-egao5r0","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密码强度用比特（bit）表示，是一个衡量密码安全性的指标。它反映了密码空间的大小，也就是密码可能的组合数量。也可以理解为：猜中密码所需的最小信息量（以二进制bit为单位）。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-hkje6sf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-hkje6sf","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举个例子：一个3位数字PIN（每位使用0"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"~"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9表示），总组合数是：10"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"^"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 1000种组合。如果用二进制表示1000种组合，至少需要log2(1000)≈9.97 bit。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-009f5a7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-009f5a7","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密码强度越高，攻击者需要尝试的组合越多，破解难度越大。强度低的密码容易被暴力破解或字典攻击。在安全设计中，密码强度比密码长度更关键，因为长度不一定代表组合多。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-v104rn1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-v104rn1","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假设：一个由62个字符（大小写字母 + 数字）组成的密码字符集，要达到AES-128的强度（128 bits），至少需要使用约22个字符，因为 log62(2"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"^"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"128)≈22。如果这些字符用UTF-8编码，则22"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"176 bits，每字符8 bits。176bit要转换成128bit的密钥使用，还需要进行转换或者截断处理。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-p0ezda9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-p0ezda9","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、什么是“熵”？"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-d8y7o1v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-d8y7o1v","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在信息论中，熵（Entropy）是衡量信息不确定性或随机性的指标。熵越高，表示数据越不可预测，也就越“随机”。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-t6fg0e6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-t6fg0e6","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个字节（byte）由8个bits组成。如果每个比特都是完全随机的，那么一个字节的最大熵就是8bits。这意味着每个可能的值（0 到 255）出现的概率是完全均等的。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-po2gqji","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-po2gqji","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（一）7.5 bits熵是什么水平？"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-dtzjkam","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-dtzjkam","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.5 bits 或更高表示数据非常接近完全随机。这意味着，虽然不是每个字节都完全均匀分布，但整体上已经足够“不可预测”，可以用于安全性要求高的场景，比如：密码学、加密密钥生成等。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-4z9hzaa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-4z9hzaa","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举例：如果用一个硬币抛8次，每次都是公平的（正反面概率各50%），那么得到的8位二进制数的熵就是8 bits。如果硬币有偏，比如正面概率是90%，那么熵就会下降，因为可以“猜”出结果，数据就不那么随机了。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-wlo1606","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-wlo1606","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（二）如何理解“at least 7.5 bits per character”"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-164wg8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-164wg8d","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"标准ASCII使用7 bits表示一个字符（扩展ASCII使用8 bits表示一个字符）。UTF-8通常使用8 bits或更多表示一个字符。在密码学中，如果一个密码或密钥的平均比特数太低，可能意味着它容易被猜测或破解。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-zbi5i6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-zbi5i6t","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果一个密码、密钥或数据字段的平均比特数低于7.5，可能被认为不够复杂或安全。要求 “at least 7.5 bits per character” 是为了确保数据具有足够的随机性和强度，从而抵抗暴力破解或字典攻击。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-113spf8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-113spf8","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（三）TRNG产生的字节熵是8bit吗"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-uc6qo9j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-uc6qo9j","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"理论上真随机数生成器（TRNG, True Random Number Generator）产生的每个字节的熵可以被视为 8 bits，但这有一些前提条件：如果TRNG的输出是完全不可预测的，并且每个字节（8 bits）中的每一位都是独立且均匀分布的。那么："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-w7fw73y","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-w7fw73y","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-9uvyrib","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-9uvyrib","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-41yxgie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-41yxgie","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个字节的熵就是8bits；"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-mu48pe2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-mu48pe2","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-c72ka1y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-c72ka1y","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该字节可以表示256种可能值，每种值的概率是1/256；"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-b4kt4mh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-b4kt4mh","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-16ig2yy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-16ig2yy","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"没有任何偏差、重复模式或可预测性。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-a35n8nr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-a35n8nr","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在现实中，TRNG 的输出可能受到以下因素影响："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-nlyo3i7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-nlyo3i7","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-4s0mif4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-4s0mif4","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-vdl1ahi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-vdl1ahi","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"硬件噪声源的质量：如热噪声、时钟抖动等；"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-y2a66yk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-y2a66yk","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-598kij5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-598kij5","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"采样机制：是否有足够的去偏处理（如使用熵提取器）；"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-uy5l8qd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-uy5l8qd","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-solyue1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-solyue1","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"统计测试结果：如NIST SP 800-90B中的熵评估方法。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-1pvy9sj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-1pvy9sj","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，实际每字节的熵可能略低于8 bits，尤其在未经充分处理的原始输出中。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-qp225xe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-qp225xe","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信息熵公式（Shannon Entropy）："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-ofr8e7u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-ofr8e7u","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"图片"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/eEEQvxEw8vxCIK9DtSTkW5ib7T9Mia9MdKNDQJqPTAAL0lVKqpS1jRQ5rYt1HS1ZcATdTicEjI04HABc1lYxWgEiag/640?wx_fmt=png\u0026from=appmsg\u0026watermark=1\u0026tp=wxpic\u0026wxfrom=5\u0026wx_lazy=1"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-xjuq7de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-xjuq7de","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-d1ft1v3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-d1ft1v3","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-6v0m8tb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-6v0m8tb","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-75y8lw0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-75y8lw0","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"H(X)表示随机变量X的熵（单位是bits）"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-hxlt4vj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-hxlt4vj","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-0tet76w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-0tet76w","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"p(xi)表示第i个符号（或字节）出现的概率"}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-5ew1353","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-5ew1353","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250828100125-fsm8ytr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-fsm8ytr","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"n表示所有可能符号的数量（对于一个字节来说是256）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-fimene3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-fimene3","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举个例子：假设有一个数据流，其中只包含4个不同的字符：A、B、C、D，它们的出现概率分别是：A: 0.25、B: 0.25、C: 0.25、D: 0.25。那么熵就是："}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-yhsgg7r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-yhsgg7r","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"H"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−(0.25log2(0.25)+0.25log2(0.25)+0.25log2(0.25)+0.25log2(0.25))"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−4×0.25×(−2)"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2bits"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-wcecr3f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-wcecr3f","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这表示每个字符平均携带2 bits的信息。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-kgr57f0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-kgr57f0","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用 ENT 工具 对熵源（entropy source）进行测试时的合格标准。ENT 是一个用于评估随机数据质量的工具，常用于测试伪随机数生成器或硬件熵源的输出。"}]},{"ID":"20250828100125-dilcw44","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250828100125-dilcw44","updated":"20250828100125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"https://www.fourmilab.ch/random/"}]}]}